<inglise> Commission Regulation (EEC) No 2746/87 of 14 September 1987 amending Regulations (EEC) No 2315/76 and (EEC) No 727/87 in respect of rules applying to the sale of butter and skimmed-milk powder from public stocks for the supply of food aid </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (EM&Uuml;) nr 2746/87, millega muudetakse m&auml;&auml;rusi (EM&Uuml;) nr 2315/76 ja (EM&Uuml;) nr 727/87 seoses riiklikest varudest p&auml;rineva v&otilde;i ning l&otilde;ssipulbri m&uuml;&uuml;gieeskirjadega toiduabi andmisel </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> 14. september 1987 EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 804/68 of 27 June 1968 on the common organization of the market in milk and milk products (1), as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 773/87 (2), and in particular Articles 6 (7) and 7 (5) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 27. juuni 1968. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 804/68 piima- ja piimatooteturu &uuml;hise korralduse kohta, viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 773/87, eriti selle artikli 6 l&otilde;iget 7 ja artikli 7 l&otilde;iget 5, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the new provisions adopted by Commission Regulation (EEC) No 2200/87 of 8 July 1987 laying down general rules for the mobilization in the Community of products to be supplied as Community food aid (3) make it compulsory in cases where supplies are mobilized from stocks held by intervention agencies for the successful tenderer to purchase the goods on price terms fixed in advance; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: komisjoni 8. juuli 1987. aasta m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 2200/87 (millega n&auml;hakse ette &uuml;ldeeskirjad toodete eraldamise ja tarnimise kohta &uuml;henduse toiduabi raames) vastuv&otilde;etud uued s&auml;tted kohustavad edukat pakkujat ostma kaupu eelnevalt kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ratud hinnaga, kui need tooted eraldatakse sekkumisasutuste valduses olevatest varudest; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Commission Regulations (EEC) No 2315/76 of 24 September 1976 on the sale of butter from public stocks (4), as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 3819/86 (5), and (EEC) No 727/87 of 13 March 1987 on a special sale of skimmed-milk powder from public stocks for export (6), laid down rules applying to the sale of these products at prices fixed in advance; whereas additions should be made to these Regulations to cover the case of purchase for supply as either Community or national food aid; whereas however in the case of purchase for this purpose certain general provisions of the said Regulations on product age, time limit for removal and lodging of securities should be waived, since the security that the successful tenderer is required to lodge under Article 12 of Regulation (EEC) No 2200/87 will also suffice to ensure fulfilment of his obligations under Regulations (EEC) No 2315/76 and (EEC) No 727/87, in particular in the case of the latter Regulation the obligation to export; </inglise>
<eesti> komisjoni 24. septembri 1976. aasta m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 2315/76 (v&otilde;i m&uuml;&uuml;gi kohta riiklikest varudest), viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 3819/86, ja 13. m&auml;rtsi 1987. aasta m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 727/87 (riiklikest varudest p&auml;rineva l&otilde;ssipulbri ekspordiks m&otilde;eldud erim&uuml;&uuml;gi kohta) n&auml;hakse ette tingimused nende toodete m&uuml;&uuml;miseks eelnevalt kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ratud hinnaga; k&otilde;nealuseid m&auml;&auml;rusi tuleks t&auml;iendada nii, et need h&otilde;lmaksid &uuml;henduse v&otilde;i riiklikuks toiduabiks etten&auml;htud oste; sel eesm&auml;rgil tehtavate ostude sooritamiseks tuleks loobuda k&otilde;nesolevate m&auml;&auml;ruste teatavatest &uuml;lds&auml;tetest toote vanuse, v&auml;ljaviimist&auml;htaja ning tagatiste esitamise kohta, v&otilde;ttes arvesse asjaolu, et tagatis, mille edukas pakkuja peab esitama vastavalt m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2200/87 artiklile 12, tagab ka tema m&auml;&auml;rusest (EM&Uuml;) nr 2315/76 ja m&auml;&auml;rusest (EM&Uuml;) nr 727/87 tulenevate kohustuste, viimasena nimetatud m&auml;&auml;ruse puhul eelk&otilde;ige ekspordikohustuse t&auml;itmise; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the amendments must, in order to ensure the proper execution of certain food aid operations, apply with effect from 10 August 1987; </inglise>
<eesti> teatavate toiduabiprogrammide n&otilde;uetekohaseks elluviimiseks tuleb muudatusi kohaldada alates 10. augustist 1987; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the opinion of the Management Committee for Milk and Milk Products, </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;rusega etten&auml;htud meetmed on vastavuses piima- ja piimatooteturu korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> The following Article is hereby inserted in Regulation (EEC) No 2315/76: </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolevaga lisatakse m&auml;&auml;rusele (EM&Uuml;) nr 2315/76 j&auml;rgmine artikkel: </eesti>
<inglise> 'Article 3a </inglise>
<eesti> "Artikkel 3a </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The provisions of Articles 1 and 2 on date of entry into store and lodging of security and of the second subparagraph of Article 3 (1) on the minimum quantity of which delivery may be taken shall not apply in the case of purchases of butter for the provision of Community food aid or for the implementation of food aid programmes decided on or recognized by the national authorities. </inglise>
<eesti> Artiklite 1 ja 2 s&auml;tteid ladustamise ja tagatise esitamise kuup&auml;evade kohta ning artikli 3 l&otilde;ike 1 teise l&otilde;igu s&auml;tteid tarnete miinimumkoguste vastuv&otilde;tmise kohta ei kohaldata &uuml;henduse toiduabi andmiseks ega siseriiklike asutuste poolt kinnitatud v&otilde;i heakskiidetud toiduabiprogrammide elluviimiseks ostetava v&otilde;i suhtes. </eesti>
<inglise> Evidence of such use shall be provided by the purchaser by means of a copy of the communication informing him that he is the successful tenderer for supply of the food aid. </inglise>
<eesti> Sellise kasutusotstarbe t&otilde;enduseks esitab ostja koopia teatisest selle kohta, et tema on tunnistatud edukaks pakkujaks toiduabi andmisel. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> Intervention agencies shall take the necessary steps to enable successful tenderers for the supply of food aid to examine at their own cost before conclusion of the purchase contract samples taken from the butter put up for sale. </inglise>
<eesti> Sekkumisasutused v&otilde;tavad vajalikke meetmeid, et toiduabi edukad pakkujad saaksid enne ostulepingu s&otilde;lmimist oma kulul tutvuda m&uuml;&uuml;dava v&otilde;i n&auml;idistega. </eesti>
<inglise> Purchasers shall waive all right of claim in connection with the quality and characteristics of the butter sold. </inglise>
<eesti> Ostjad loobuvad &otilde;igusest esitada kaebusi m&uuml;&uuml;dud v&otilde;i kvaliteedi ja omaduste kohta. </eesti>
<inglise> 3. </inglise>
<eesti> 3. </eesti>
<inglise> The conversion rate applicable in the case of supplies for food aid covered by this Article shall be the representative rate valid on the last day for the submission of tenders for the supply in question. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esoleva artikliga h&otilde;lmatud toiduabihangete suhtes kohaldatav &uuml;mberarvestuskurss on k&otilde;nesoleva hankega seotud pakkumiste viimasel esitamisp&auml;eval kehtiv kurss. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> The following Article 6a is hereby inserted in Regulation (EEC) No 727/87: </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolevaga lisatakse m&auml;&auml;rusele (EM&Uuml;) nr 727/87 artikkel 6a: </eesti>
<inglise> 'Article 6a </inglise>
<eesti> "Artikkel 6a </eesti>
<inglise> The provisions of Article 2 (1) shall also apply to the sale of skimmed-milk powder from public stocks for the supply of Community food aid or for the implementation of food aid programmes decided on or recognized by national authorities. </inglise>
<eesti> Artikli 2 l&otilde;ike 1 s&auml;tteid kohaldatakse ka riiklikest varudest p&auml;rineva l&otilde;ssipulbri m&uuml;&uuml;gi suhtes &uuml;henduse toiduabi andmiseks v&otilde;i siseriiklike ametiasutuste poolt kinnitatud v&otilde;i heakskiidetud toiduabiprogrammide elluviimiseks. </eesti>
<inglise> However, in such cases: </inglise>
<eesti> Niisugustel juhtudel: </eesti>
<inglise> (a) the provisions of Article 1 on date of entry into stock, of Article 2 (2) on minimum quantity, of Articles 2 (2) and 4 (1) on securities and of Article 9 shall not be applicable; </inglise>
<eesti> a) ei kohaldata siiski artikli 1 s&auml;tteid ladustamiskuup&auml;eva kohta, artikli 2 l&otilde;ike 2 s&auml;tteid miinimumkoguse kohta, artikli 2 l&otilde;ike 2 ja artikli 4 l&otilde;ike 1 s&auml;tteid tagatiste kohta ega artiklit 9; </eesti>
<inglise> (b) Article 4 (3) notwithstanding, the purchaser shall pay the intervention agency before removal for each lot removed; </inglise>
<eesti> b) olenemata artikli 4 l&otilde;ikest 3, tasub ostja sekkumisasutusele v&auml;ljaviidavate kaubapartiide eest enne nende v&auml;ljaviimist; </eesti>
<inglise> (c) Article 7 notwithstanding, the conversion rate applicable shall be the representative rate valid on the last day for submission of tenders for the supply in question. </inglise>
<eesti> c) hoolimata artiklist 7, on &uuml;mberarvestuskursiks k&otilde;nesoleva hankega seotud pakkumiste viimasel esitamisp&auml;eval kehtiv kurss." </eesti>
<inglise> Article 3 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the day following its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub p&auml;ev p&auml;rast selle avaldamist Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas. </eesti>
<inglise> The provisions referred to in Articles 1 and 2 shall apply with effect from 10 August 1987. </inglise>
<eesti> Artiklites 1 ja 2 nimetatud s&auml;tteid kohaldatakse alates 10. augustist 1987. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 14 September 1987. </inglise>
<eesti> Br&uuml;ssel, 14. september 1987 </eesti>
